hopobject.body: Could you tell me my balance, please? discount paxil cr Do not make the mistake of assuming that all the restaurants in a big hotel will be of the same standard. Palm Tree Court sat in the same compound as the Jebel Ali Beach Hotel, meaning that guests were able to use the restaurants and facilities of both interchangeably. But it took us half the week to work out that the food next door was better. After that, we ended up eating there almost exclusively.
